{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_05_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 ここが噂のスタジオですね！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "まいったな……まさかドッキリ番組から\n千紗にオファーがくるとは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh no… I can't believe an offer came for Chisa from a prank show…\nI never thought she'd get an offer like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2633.3333333000005,
          "startTime": 6.7
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、{user}さん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（しかも「ホラー好きを公言するアイドルは）\n（本当に幽霊を怖がらないのか」検証する企画って……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(And it's a segment about)\n(\"Can an idol who claims to love horror really not be scared by ghosts?\"…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（ようは千紗に心霊ドッキリを仕掛けて）\n（怖がらせるってことだよな？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(In other words‚ they're planning to set up a supernatural prank on Chisa…)\n(To scare her‚ right?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん？\nあれ、おかしいな。聞こえてるよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san?\nHuh‚ that's strange. You can hear me‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（番組スタッフは、どんなにホラー好きでも実際に）\n（恐怖体験をすれば怖がると思っているようだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Even though the program staff might believe that even a horror enthusiast…)\n(Will get scared when actually facing a fearful experience…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（千紗のホラー耐性は筋金入りだ）\n（全然怖がらなくて番組が成り立たない可能性も……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Chisa's resistance to horror is solid.)\n(If she doesn't get scared at all‚ the show might not work…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "うわぁっ！　びっくりした……なんだ、千紗か",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoa! You scared me… Oh‚ it's you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "びっくりしたのはこっちです\n無視されてるのかと思っちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was the one surprised.\nI thought you were ignoring me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あ……すまない、ちょっと考えごとをしていたんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Sorry‚ I was lost in thought for a moment.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（とにかくやるしかない。千紗を騙すのは心苦しいが）\n（テレビ番組に出演するためだ。許してくれ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I have no choice but to do this. Tricking Chisa is uncomfortable‚ but…)\n(It's for the sake of appearing on a TV show. Please forgive me…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "実は、千紗にテレビCMの出演依頼が来ているんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ Chisa has received an offer to appear in a TV commercial.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　サニピじゃなくて私一人にですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh!? Not as part of Sunny Peace‚ just me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "撮影ではかなりの負担を強いることになると思う\nもし不安なら断っても構わないが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The shoot will be quite demanding‚ I imagine.\nIf you're feeling unsure‚ you can decline…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、やりたいです！　やらせて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I want to do it! Please let me do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "私に期待してオファーしてくれたんですよね？\n私はその期待に応えたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They offered this to me with expectations‚ right?\nI want to live up to those expectations.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "（期待されているのは、ドッキリで怖がる姿だけどな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(The expectations are for her to get scared during the prank…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "それで、私がやるのはなんのCMなんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ what kind of commercial will I be doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "新作ゲームのテレビCMだ。宣伝に力を入れていて\n撮影時には情報番組の取材も入るらしい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's for a new game's TV commercial. They're putting a lot of effort into promotion…\nThere might also be coverage by a news program during the shoot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "CM撮影の様子を取材するんですね\nそういうの見たことあります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're going to cover the making of the commercial‚ right?\nI've seen those before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、ひょっとしたら全国ネットの朝の情報番組で\n私の顔と名前が紹介されるかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ maybe my face and name will be\nintroduced on a nationwide morning news show…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "（すまない。千紗が出るのは朝の情報番組じゃなくて）\n（夜のバラエティ番組なんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Sorry. Chisa won't be appearing on a morning news show…)\n(It's actually a late-night variety show.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく大変な仕事だから、覚悟だけはしておいてくれ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's going to be a challenging job‚ so be prepared.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました！\nどんな撮影でも、頑張って最後までやり遂げます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood!\nNo matter the shoot‚ I'll give it my all till the end!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ドッキリ撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Day of the prank",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 147
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよこれからCM撮影ですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's finally time for the CM shoot‚ isn't it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 152.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "表情が硬いが、緊張しているのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Your expression is tense. Are you nervous?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "実は昨日、お仕事で優ちゃんと同じ楽屋になって……\nそこで聞いちゃったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ I was in the same waiting room as Yu-chan for work yesterday…\nAnd there‚ I overheard something…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 164.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_05_01-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "今日の撮影で使うスタジオって……出るらしいんです",
      "translations": {
